SENATE BILL DRS35334-MGa-172
Short Title: Reduce County Share/SA In-Home Program. (Public)
Sponsors: Senator Lowe (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT APPROPRIATING FUNDS TO THE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND HUMAN
3 SERVICES, DIVISION OF SOCIAL SERVICES, TO REDUCE THE COUNTY SHARE
4 OF PAYMENTS FOR THE STATE-COUNTY SPECIAL ASSISTANCE IN-HOME
5 PROGRAM.
6 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
7 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Department of
8 Health and Human Services, Division of Social Services, the sum of five hundred thousand
9 dollars ($500,000) in recurring funds beginning with the 2026-2027 fiscal year to reduce the
10 county share of payments for the State-County Special Assistance in-home program.
11 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2026.
*DRS35334-MGa-172*

